奥斯type既deep lying play maker<br />\n不過只係同類 依家既佢差同上面兩個好撚多班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但點都唔可以怪哂佢 雲加根本唔識教佢<br />\n淨係上面兩個有基迪拉 維度爾 卡斯米路係身邊做dirty work已經差好遠<br />\n<br />\n呢類球員其實我覺得佢地個防務工作首要係delay對面反擊 遮線同technical foul多過真係落腳去 但xhaka就成日忽上腦一野掃落去同沙比個啲陰陰濕濕拉下衫完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋xhaka 最大個問題係cool唔到波 俾人一迫就甩好似當個波炸彈咁傳出去 睇得多阿狗就明一受壓就面對面都交失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢一點係佢打呢個位最大既問題你點會成日見到沙比卻奥斯會俾人迫甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63efaa6602ae3c5c3cbbe6e5ae2d743841d51558","tid":518943,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f97cb6750d7539f8903c4a02e9a0c92c6d1ae3a","tid":518943,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ecddaa5927344a60a1139b136fbea72f8d94cd","tid":518943,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c6398b10e7cb66ffd21bdd817c81fd52814e58","tid":518943,"uid":164266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"講咁耐 我真係好掛住桑治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"但你諗下song屌左幾多年先打到1，2季好波，然後就話要去巴菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"但係佢真係打得好好，場場長傳比RVP窩利入波，直線放得靚，夠硬淨，我覺得阿仙奴需要佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T18:37:30.000Z","msg":"又印象球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失唔少位啦"},{"pid":"1c92f2def89d45ab5ac79aa1ecb17dfaf9725fcf","tid":518943,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d469b70d60b633b5188820144f585ae6e7248de0","t